These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Game: poker, mah-jongg, domino, backgammon
Nationality: french, nigerian, argentine, pakistani
1. Game:domino is between Nationality:argentine and Nationality:nigerian##2
2. Game:backgammon is on the left or right of Nationality:argentine##3
3. Nationality:argentine is not to the left of Nationality:argentine##8
4. Nationality:nigerian != Game:domino##6
5. Game:domino is somewhere to the right of Game:poker##5
6. Game:poker is on the right of Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | backgammon  | poker | domino | mah-jongg  |
| Nationality   | french | argentine   | pakistani  | nigerian |

