.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Sport: cricket, baseball, skiing, badminton
Movie-Genre: epic, musical, satire, horror
1. Movie-Genre:horror is not to the left of Movie-Genre:horror##8
2. Sport:cricket is somewhere to the right of Sport:badminton##5
3. Sport:cricket == Movie-Genre:musical##1
4. Sport:badminton is between Sport:cricket and Sport:baseball##2
5. Sport:baseball is somewhere between Sport:skiing and Movie-Genre:epic##7
6. Movie-Genre:satire is somewhere to the left of Sport:baseball##5
7. Movie-Genre:epic is not to the left of Movie-Genre:epic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skiing | baseball          | badminton | cricket     |
| Movie-Genre    | satire      | horror | epic | musical |

