.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Cigar: pall-mall, bongani, bluemaster, alhambra
City: nizza, venice, boston, hamburg
1. City:nizza is not to the left of Cigar:bluemaster##8
2. City:venice is on the far left##1
3. Cigar:bongani is on the right of Cigar:pall-mall##1
4. Cigar:bongani is in an even position##4
5. Cigar:alhambra is on the far left or far right##3
6. Cigar:pall-mall is somewhere to the left of City:hamburg##5
7. Cigar:alhambra == City:boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | bongani | bluemaster     | alhambra |
| City   | venice    | hamburg   | nizza | boston    |

