2. Pet:cat is not to the left of Pet:turtle##8
3. Pet:mouse is on the right of House:townhouse##1
4. House:victorian is not to the right of Pet:mouse##8
5. House:wooden == Pet:cat##1
6. House:wooden is on the right of Pet:mouse##1
7. House:tower is somewhere to the left of House:victorian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| House   | tower   | townhouse         | victorian   | wooden    |
| Pet         | turtle | lizard | mouse | cat |

